height=48 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334690/extras/42cda19a75b9f8e2fbe8c39f30621768.webp?t=1762061852\" width=48 height=48 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334690/extras/3826275ba602e867b25bd3e8f668f58a.webp?t=1762061852\" width=48 height=48 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334690/extras/03226e169f2b089236285742e35da63a.webp?t=1762061852\" width=48 height=48 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334690/extras/3826275ba602e867b25bd3e8f668f58a.webp?t=1762061852\" width=48 height=48 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334690/extras/42cda19a75b9f8e2fbe8c39f30621768.webp?t=1762061852\" width=48 height=48 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334690/extras/3826275ba602e867b25bd3e8f668f58a.webp?t=1762061852\" width=48 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334690/extras/d120bed60076cd9c263d2a875278bfb2.webp?t=1762061852\" width=18 height=18 /></span>THE EPIC TAIL SO FAR<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334690/extras/d120bed60076cd9c263d2a875278bfb2.webp?t=1762061852\" width=18 height=18 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious robotic squirrel - Shadow-tail, has kidnapped the squirrels and stolen all their gems and acorns. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat him and his powerful machines to take back planet Squirreltopia and prevent squirrel extinction!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334690/extras/d120bed60076cd9c263d2a875278bfb2.webp?t=1762061852\" width=18 height=18 /></span>SQUIRRELLY GAMEPLAY<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334690/extras/d120bed60076cd9c263d2a875278bfb2.webp?t=1762061852\" width=18 height=18 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scurry across 50 levels and take control of a random squirrel each time. Every level is designed to have its own look and feel, and push squirrel physics to the limit. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334690/extras/d120bed60076cd9c263d2a875278bfb2.webp?t=1762061852\" width=18 height=18 /></span>Addictive momentum-based gameplay <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334690/extras/d120bed60076cd9c263d2a875278bfb2.webp?t=1762061852\" width=18 height=18 /></span>♫ Full Original Soundtrack  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334690/extras/d120bed60076cd9c263d2a875278bfb2.webp?t=1762061852\" width=18 height=18 /></span>Insane Boss battles  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334690/extras/d120bed60076cd9c263d2a875278bfb2.webp?t=1762061852\" width=18 height=18 /></span>Play as a new Squirrel each level and every life! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334690/extras/d120bed60076cd9c263d2a875278bfb2.webp?t=1762061852\" width=18 height=18 /></span>Cutting-edge squirrel tail physics!   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334690/extras/d120bed60076cd9c263d2a875278bfb2.webp?t=1762061852\" width=18 height=18 /></span>Explore the overworld and find entrances to new levels, play in any order!   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334690/extras/d120bed60076cd9c263d2a875278bfb2.webp?t=1762061852\" width=18 height=18 /></span>Mini-games, unlocked by finding retro game cartridges hidden in levels   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334690/extras/d120bed60076cd9c263d2a875278bfb2.webp?t=1762061852\" width=18 height=18 /></span>Scurry fast and try to earn the time trophies!   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334690/extras/d120bed60076cd9c263d2a875278bfb2.webp?t=1762061852\" width=18 height=18 /></span>Secret cheat items that can only be earned by the most skilled Squirrels!   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/334690/extras/d120bed60076cd9c263d2a875278bfb2.webp?t=1762061852\" width=18 height=18 /></span>Can play with only 1 hand   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have the squirrel skills to handle it?</p>",
